<p><span class="anchor" id="p52"></span>بِيَمِينِهِ<a href="#p52" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p53"></span>وَلَو اشْترى<a href="#p53" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p54"></span>أَحدهمَا شَيْئا<a href="#p54" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p55"></span>وَقَالَ اشْتَرَيْته للشَّرِكَة أَو لنَفْسي وَكذبه الآخر<a href="#p55" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p56"></span>بِأَن عكس مَا قَالَه<a href="#p56" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p57"></span>صدق المُشْتَرِي<a href="#p57" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
